{"type": "email", "id": "email_001", "subject": "Compliance strategy meeting agenda for Q4 2028", "from": "priya.patel@mediconn.com", "from_name": "Dr. Priya Patel", "to": ["james.martin@mediconn.com", "robert.johnson@mediconn.com"], "cc": ["linda.garcia@mediconn.com"], "date": "2028-09-01 10:00:00", "body": "Dear James and Robert,

As you know, the federal government’s 2025 interpretation of the Canada Health Act (CHA) presents significant compliance risks for MediConn. To address these risks, we need to consider both legal precedents and provincial variations. We will be having a meeting to discuss these issues in detail next week.

Regards,
Dr. Priya Patel", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
